n<br />\n6K夠，14年5.7K係肥花買左個1號腳連波頭"},{"pid":"78ce357beb1960508e7da41a5bb395a010bc076d","tid":38694,"uid":49858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>接受到2手又自己接受到的話就買啦，全新gitzo 貴到唔合理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔合理咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用部2,3萬既機，配支雞腳仲唔合理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前抵買囉，而家堅唔抵，以一支2號腳為例，全新起碼要5k尾6k頭，講緊淨腳，未計個頭，你買得支gitzo唔會買個雞頭掛，平的photoclam, 靚少少的就markin, 再上就arca swiss/ rrs, 連埋快拆板/ L架的話成萬蚊落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2手6k的話已經夠買腳連頭，抵玩好多<br />\n<br />\n利申：G牌長期用家，入門果陣新的1227mk2都只係2k頭一支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8540257e34f89433d443ce2092b85fe0115d786","tid":38694,"uid":49858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如你儲多d錢 因為一支靚腳 用好耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6K夠，14年5.7K係肥花買左個1號腳連波頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1號腳大風點會腳軟，有另一支主腳的話無所謂，做主腳的話起碼2號會好好多"},{"pid":"9ad0f1d83bf0431718bf91b752f0397e1fc7d3b8","tid":38694,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"買乜都好，千奇唔好連支嫂波頭。"},{"pid":"75c85b35f2c9e40f049ff2dbe8d26e8060c69b0f","tid":38694,"uid":49858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買乜都好，千奇唔好連支嫂波頭。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心聲，搵人笨的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fb3d21f1d4b9f583c7820031d517c35e645dd1","tid":38694,"uid":2123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買乜都好，千奇唔好連支嫂波頭。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n心聲，搵人笨的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 